{
  "texts": [
    "We have also tested the attack performances under defenses like perplexity filtering (Alon and Kamfonas, 2023), RA-LLM (Cao et al., 2023) and Llama Guard (Inan et al., 2023).",
    "The experimenting details can be found in Appendix H, and Table 12 showed that our attack introduces little extra per-plexity while preserving the most ASR when the defenses are in place, implying strong resistance.",
    "In this paper, we have proposed a novel strategy for jailbreaking attacks to breach safety guardrails both more effectively and more efficiently.",
    "The proposed method exploits the vulnerabilities within the current safety alignment procedure and uses both query and response obfuscation simultaneously for the best attack performances.",
    "Extensive experiments demonstrate that the proposed attack can break the guardrails of the current leading proprietary and open-source LLMs, including the latest Claude 3, GPT 4, and Llama 3 models."
  ]
}